title: OCVarsity On the Record: Stallions stun, storms brew in Week 5
text:
OCVarsity On the Record: Stallions stun, storms brew in Week 5 October 01, 2015 2:33 PM BY BRIAN WHITEHEAD AND DAMIAN CALHOUN STAFF WRITERS 
Welcome back to OCVarsity On the Record with Brian Whitehead and Damian Calhoun! 
This week, the guys discuss San Juan Hills' astounding romp of Los Alamitos in Week 4 and the Stallions' ensuing leap in Monday's OCVarsity rankings. 
Plus: Why doesn't Damian believe in JSerra yet? Should we be talking more about a possible San Clemente resurgence? Can La Habra be beat in the Freeway League? And why do Westminster (4-0) and Garden Grove (3-1) keep plummeting in the Southern Division coaches poll? 
Oh, and Damian muses on Orange County volleyball for the first time this season. 
All this and more on OCVarsity On the Record!
